---
title: Grilled Harissa-Spiced Chicken Tenders with Veggie Bulgur and Lemon-Garlic Yogurt Sauce
description: Earthy and warm harissa-coated chicken tenders get fire-licked on the grill for that irresistible smoky profile we missed all winter long. Lightly charred sweet peppers grilled alongside the chicken get chopped and tossed with nutty bulgur for tasty side and a lemony, garlicky yogurt drizzle finishes the plate off with some pizzazz!
